lyrics:
[Verse]
There was a man from White Church, his name was Philly More (Philly More)
By the age of only twenty, he had his hair no more (no more hair)
He's Arsenal's number one fan, he's got a fire in his soul (oh yeah)
When he's in the stands, you know he's gonna lose control (lose control, yeah yeah)

[Chorus]
Philly More, rockin' on the floor (rockin', rockin')
He's the king of football, you can't ignore (can't ignore)
With his chants and cheers, he'll bring you to the core (bring you to the core)
Philly More, gotta hear him roar (oh yeah)
Philly More, yeah yeah yeah
Philly More, gonna win the score (win the score)
